{"tid":1016762,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"窗簾有冇的係防塵既？","createTime":"2019-02-11T03:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T13:11:54.000Z","uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"95afe62d05690e8fd128ff7dbc7b90e541cf2655","tid":1016762,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:05:03.000Z","msg":"全能既爸絲打，有冇可能有的窗簾/玻璃貼，可以滿足以下既要求：-<br />\n<br />\n1. 防塵（唔使成日洗，兩星期吸一次塵都得）<br />\n2. 防光 （唔驚人望到，因為對面屋好遠，唔會睇到，純緒想瞓既時候暗的）<br />\n3. 夠輕 （唔想打釘）<br />\n<br />\n而家諗住上半段用的鐵筒加塊布，下半段用防光玻璃貼，因為上半段個的布應該輕同易洗的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家有冇的新idea分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba9f32cfe1af4a3aa10ca5410cba0e3a23ba4a7","tid":1016762,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"b7e3f607bb47a3c4182821d1c0a159e6fefdb344","tid":1016762,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"用電子啦"},{"pid":"b6742e05b5c46ca244ba6752c6e8604a40635ebb","tid":1016762,"uid":123789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:23:39.000Z","msg":"除左布之外既窗簾都係防塵，因為冇得洗。例如捲簾、百葉簾等等..."},{"pid":"74abe52331b7ed9d838199fb9e83daf61336c3e3","tid":1016762,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4f9aa3c8b9262642aefcc7ce9bc7a5647fdd07","tid":1016762,"uid":182067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7e3f607bb47a3c4182821d1c0a159e6fefdb344","tid":1016762,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"用電子啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T06:53:54.000Z","msg":"有冇多的資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 